msgid "Styles: Applying\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:5
msgid "[2 of 6](Styles-Creating.html)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:9
msgid ""
"Applying a style adds the tools it contains to the top of the [tool "
"stack](Tool_Stack.html) for either the photo being edited or one or more "
"photos selected in the [Photo Browser](Anatomy-Browser.html)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:11
msgid "![image](images/Styles-Preview-en.png)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "To apply a style to the photo being edited:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1.  '
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:24
msgid "Select the Styles tab."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '2.  '
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:24
msgid ""
"Preview a style by moving the mouse over its name. As you do, the smaller "
"version of your photo above the styles will show what your photo would look "
"like if the style were applied."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '3.  '
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:24
msgid "To apply the style to your photo, click the name of the style."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '4.  '
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:24
msgid ""
"Alternatively, if you know exactly which style you want to apply, select "
"File \\> Apply Style \\> and the name of the style that you want to "
"apply. (The tools from the style will then be added to the top of the [tool "
"stack](Tool_Stack.html).)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "To apply a style to the one or more photos in the browser:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '1.  '
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:36
msgid ""
"Select one or more thumbnails of the photos that you want to apply a style "
"to. (Use the Shift key to select multiple, contiguous thumbnails or the "
"Command Control key to select multiple, non-contiguous thumbnails.)"
msgstr "Select one or more thumbnails of the photos that you want to apply a style to. (Shift キーを使って複数の連続したサムネイルを選択するか、Command キーまたは Ctrl キーを使って複数のとびとびになったサムネイルを選択します。)"

#. type: Bullet: '2.  '
#: Styles-Applying.markdown.txt:36
msgid ""
"Select Browser \\> Apply Style \\> and the name of the style that you want "
"to apply. (The tools from the style will then be added to the top of the "
"[tool stack](Tool_Stack.html) for all the selected photos.)"
msgstr ""
